cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.DS 

This paper combines multiple evolutionary algorithms to solve symbolic regression problems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the use of black-box optimization and exploration/exploitation trade-offs could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper involves optimization and search algorithms, which could also place it in cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
